      "description": "# ğŸ“Š Team Statistics - Advanced Locals\n\n**Grouping drivers by team:**\n```hcl\ndrivers_by_team = {\n  for team in [\"velocity-racing\", ...] : team => [\n    for driver_key, driver in var.drivers : driver_key\n    if driver.team == team\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**What this creates:** A map where each team has a list of their drivers - perfect for analysis and reporting! ğŸ“ˆ"
